  "lines": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "It was a sunny morning in a small town, and the air smelled like fresh bread.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "A woman, a man, a child, and two kind elders planned a simple walk to the park.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "The park had a big tree, a tiny pond, and a red bench that everyone loved.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "roleId": 5,
      "line": "Let us take the easy path today, the one with the flowers.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "roleId": 1,
      "line": "Yes, and we can count the butterflies as we go.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "roleId": 0,
      "line": "Can I bring my little blue bucket?",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "roleId": 3,
      "line": "Of course, dear. You might find a shiny leaf to carry home.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "roleId": 4,
      "line": "And if we are lucky, we will see a duck.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "They walked slowly and happily, looking at the bright flowers along the path.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "The child skipped once, then twice, and held the bucket with both hands.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "roleId": 0,
      "line": "I see a yellow flower. It looks like the sun.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "roleId": 5,
      "line": "Yes, and the sun is smiling at us today.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "roleId": 1,
      "line": "Let us keep going, the pond is just ahead.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "roleId": 3,
      "line": "We can sit and rest by the water.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "roleId": 4,
      "line": "Rest is good, especially with a nice view.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "At the pond, the water was calm and clear.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "A little duck swam in a slow circle, then stopped to look at them.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "roleId": 0,
      "line": "Hello, duck. Do you want to play?",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "roleId": 4,
      "line": "The duck says, quack, and that means hello.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "roleId": 3,
      "line": "We can wave with our hands and say hello too.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "roleId": 5,
      "line": "Let us be gentle and quiet, so the duck feels safe.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "roleId": 1,
      "line": "We can sit on the red bench and watch.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "They sat together, and the child swung their feet above the grass.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "roleId": 0,
      "line": "I will count: one duck, two rocks, three clouds.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "roleId": 5,
      "line": "That is a good count.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "roleId": 1,
      "line": "You are a careful watcher.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "roleId": 3,
      "line": "A careful watcher sees kind things.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "roleId": 4,
      "line": "And a kind heart makes the day bright.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "After a while, they walked home with easy steps.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "The child carried a shiny leaf in the blue bucket.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "roleId": 0,
      "line": "I will show it to my teddy.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "roleId": 5,
      "line": "That will make teddy happy.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "roleId": 1,
      "line": "It is a good leaf for a good day.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "roleId": 3,
      "line": "A simple day can be the best day.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "roleId": 4,
      "line": "Yes, and tomorrow we can come again.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "roleId": 2,
      "line": "They waved to the park, and the park seemed to wave back.",
      "extra": null,
      "actorId": null
    }
  ]
}